18:04.317 --> 18:05.216
Cass.

18:05.652 --> 18:06.684
Yeah?

18:08.321 --> 18:09.754
Did you hear
anything last night?

18:11.357 --> 18:12.457
No, like what?

18:14.494 --> 18:16.661
- Anything weird?
- No.

18:17.664 --> 18:18.796
Okay.

18:19.532 --> 18:21.099
See you when you wake up.

18:21.101 --> 18:21.799
Bye.

18:45.125 --> 18:46.491
It's going to be okay.

18:46.493 --> 18:50.194
Do you hear me? And don't
you even worry about work.

18:50.196 --> 18:51.762
Sarah's got you covered.

18:51.764 --> 18:54.699
We can get as many
extensions as we need.

18:57.604 --> 18:59.270
Do you need anything else?

19:01.774 --> 19:03.741
Let's go. Get a cup
of coffee or something.

19:16.489 --> 19:17.688
Get out of my house.

19:17.690 --> 19:19.590
Danni. Danni, come
here. You're upset.

19:19.592 --> 19:22.210
- I'll make you some--
- Get off me.

19:22.211 --> 19:24.829
Hey! This is my house too. All right?
Don't make a scene in front of all these people.

19:24.831 --> 19:27.198
I don't give a shit
about these people.

19:27.199 --> 19:29.566
Do they know how I feel? Do
they actually care? Do you care?

19:29.569 --> 19:32.336
- Do you actually care?
- Of course, I care!

19:32.338 --> 19:33.804
Girl, come with me.

19:34.440 --> 19:35.773
I'm sorry.

19:45.485 --> 19:46.817
Everyone out.

19:47.487 --> 19:49.687
Get the fuck out of my house!

19:50.557 --> 19:51.889
Get out!

19:53.226 --> 19:54.692
You did this.

19:57.430 --> 19:58.462
Sorry.

20:42.675 --> 20:43.608
Hey.

20:44.611 --> 20:45.776
What are you doing?

20:47.013 --> 20:48.012
Um...

20:49.916 --> 20:52.817
I'm just checking out
your cool setup here.

20:53.419 --> 20:54.619
Okay.

20:55.488 --> 20:57.788
- What's it for?
- My safe house.

21:01.294 --> 21:03.361
Why do you feel you
need a safe house?

21:04.597 --> 21:06.764
- You don't feel safe at home?
- I don't know.

21:06.766 --> 21:10.434
Sometimes I like to be alone,
or when I walk during my sleep.

21:11.504 --> 21:13.304
I sometimes end up out here.

21:13.773 --> 21:15.573
How often does that happen?

21:16.376 --> 21:19.477
I've been keeping track.
When I wear the face,

21:19.479 --> 21:22.280
all the bad stuff
seems to stay away.

21:22.282 --> 21:24.582
It's hard wearing it
all the time, though.

21:24.584 --> 21:26.350
Maybe you can make me one.

21:27.787 --> 21:29.920
I could use some help
keeping the bad stuff away.

21:30.890 --> 21:34.025
So, what sounds good to eat?

21:34.027 --> 21:38.896
We could get something
delivered or we could go out.

21:39.966 --> 21:42.900
When was the last time we did that, huh?
I could use a good excuse to shave.

21:42.902 --> 21:43.768
Look at that.

21:44.404 --> 21:45.503
Not that hungry.

21:45.505 --> 21:47.905
Come on, Cass, you
got to eat something.

21:47.907 --> 21:49.573
I'm okay really.

21:54.013 --> 21:55.313
Okay.

21:57.583 --> 21:58.749
All right.

23:58.704 --> 24:00.354
So what are you saying?

24:00.355 --> 24:02.005
Just saying you guys
should get a hotel tonight.

24:03.075 --> 24:04.475
<i>What about Cassie?</i>

24:06.012 --> 24:07.845
I'll get some more clothes.

24:08.214 --> 24:09.613
Tomorrow's Friday, right?

24:09.615 --> 24:12.817
Maybe I can pick her up.
She can spend the weekend with me.

24:16.856 --> 24:17.888
Or not.

24:19.158 --> 24:21.025
You know this is still
your home, right?

24:21.027 --> 24:23.461
I do want see her
sometime soon, okay?

24:25.097 --> 24:26.130
I mean,

24:26.132 --> 24:30.201
actually I got to head up north for work in a couple of days.
Quick trip.

24:30.203 --> 24:32.169
Close a couple of contract.
Maybe she can tag along.

24:32.171 --> 24:34.205
I'm just saying you
still have a key.

24:34.207 --> 24:37.241
I just don't understand
wasting money on a hotel.

24:37.844 --> 24:39.710
<i>I'm not the one</i>
<i>who's doing this.</i>

24:39.712 --> 24:42.079
You asked me to leave, remember?

24:44.884 --> 24:46.050
I just-

24:48.788 --> 24:50.955
I just need some
time, okay? I-- I--

24:52.225 --> 24:53.824
reorganize my brain.

24:55.094 --> 24:56.560
<i>We can figure this out.</i>

24:58.164 --> 24:59.196
Okay.

25:02.902 --> 25:04.068
<i>Danni, wait, wait, wait.</i>

25:04.070 --> 25:06.737
I have-- I have to finish
cleaning up, so.

25:08.107 --> 25:09.607
Look, I'm sorry.

25:09.609 --> 25:10.574
Hey, it's-

25:12.278 --> 25:16.814
this is just going to get better.
I just-- after everything-

25:17.984 --> 25:20.117
I can forgive you, Michael.

25:20.620 --> 25:21.752
I have.

25:21.754 --> 25:25.856
I'm trying to let it go. Why
can't you do the same?

25:30.296 --> 25:32.062
I'll talk to you later, okay?

25:37.870 --> 25:38.903
Fuck.

