<i>In actuality, we all experience</i>
<i>a few common ones from the list.</i>

26:22.648 --> 26:25.716
<i>People fall asleep and wake up</i>
<i>in random parts of their home.</i>

26:26.052 --> 26:28.052
<i>They fall asleep at the</i>
<i>wheel while driving.</i>

26:28.654 --> 26:30.888
<i>For those who are</i>
<i>an narcoleptic of course.</i>

26:30.890 --> 26:32.823
<i>Take sleep paralysis,</i>
<i>for instance.</i>

26:32.825 --> 26:37.695
<i>People claim to see these intruders in</i>
<i>their home where they feel defenseless.</i>

26:37.697 --> 26:42.766
