<i>it's an apparition or something demonic.</i>

26:43.235 --> 26:48.205
<i>But most of the time it is because you are still half asleep.</i>

26:48.207 --> 26:51.609
<i>Grief is a very, very</i>
<i>powerful emotion.</i>

26:52.612 --> 26:56.213
