<i>You can't do that.</i>

34:15.286 --> 34:17.054
<i>Why not?</i>

34:18.056 --> 34:20.456
<i>Because</i>
<i>it wouldn't be right.</i>

34:21.293 --> 34:24.226
<i>Yes, it would.</i>

34:24.228 --> 34:27.130
<i>I'm not going to</i>
