<i>She was there.</i>

34:31.469 --> 34:34.137
<i>She allowed it to happen.</i>

34:35.507 --> 34:37.574
<i>She couldn't do</i>
<i>anything about it.</i>

34:38.143 --> 34:40.310
<i>But you can.</i>

34:40.646 --> 34:46.083
<i>You can do something</i>
<i>about it now.</i>

34:47.319 --> 34:50.353
<i>- Aren't you angry?</i>
