34:50.355 --> 34:53.223
<i>Aren't you mad? Get out.</i>

34:53.659 --> 34:55.692
<i>Get out and fucking</i>
<i>die. Get out.</i>

34:55.694 --> 34:57.227
<i>Get out. Get out!</i>

34:57.229 --> 34:59.429
<i>Shut up</i>
<i>and leave me alone.</i>

34:59.798 --> 35:02.632
<i>Get out.</i>
<i>Get out and destroy her.</i>

35:02.634 --> 35:04.267
<i>Destroy her family.</i>

35:04.269 --> 35:06.636
<i>Go and fucking</i>
<i>kill her. Get out.</i>

35:07.306 --> 35:08.605
<i>You punk.</i>

35:08.607 --> 35:10.440
<i>Fucking whore.</i>

35:10.809 --> 35:12.709
Is that my phone?

35:12.711 --> 35:15.579
Cassie, what's going on?
Why are you filming these?

35:15.581 --> 35:17.381
Give me my phone, please?

35:17.382 --> 35:19.182
Who are you talking to?
You're scaring me.

35:19.184 --> 35:21.018
