down my neck sometimes.

37:32.584 --> 37:35.285
- Really? Are you serious?
- I don't know.

37:35.287 --> 37:37.821
I can't explain it, but
there is a presence.

37:37.823 --> 37:40.324
It's-- I swear to
God, I'm not crazy.

37:40.325 --> 37:42.826
