it feels like every night.

37:42.828 --> 37:44.494
Well, sometimes
I see things too.

37:44.496 --> 37:46.897
- I'm really tired.
- Yeah, but there's seeing

37:46.898 --> 37:49.299
and then there's feeling, Michael,
I physically feel this presence.

37:49.935 --> 37:50.867
Kiddo.

37:52.037 --> 37:53.403
Have fun.

37:54.873 --> 37:56.506
I'll have her back tomorrow.

37:56.508 --> 37:57.841
Got a couple of meetings
in the morning.

37:57.843 --> 37:59.709
She promised to suck
it up and wait on.

38:01.813 --> 38:03.513
- Thanks for this.
- Yeah.

38:05.384 --> 38:06.449
Good night.

38:07.019 --> 38:07.917
Michael.

38:08.987 --> 38:09.953
Yeah.

38:11.723 --> 38:14.624
Nothing. It's just--
Uh, we'll talk later.

38:15.694 --> 38:16.660
All right.

38:20.032 --> 38:21.431
I don't know.

38:22.301 --> 38:23.933
She's just so hard to
communicate with.

38:23.935 --> 38:26.636
And now she's talking
to herself in her sleep.

38:27.639 --> 38:28.905
How do I even deal with that?

38:28.907 --> 38:30.640
<i>Have you</i>
<i>considered counseling?</i>

38:30.642 --> 38:33.410
- For me or for her?
- Maybe all three of y'all.

38:34.513 --> 38:35.979
God, we'd never--

38:36.782 --> 38:38.815
And Cassie won't even
look me in the eyes anymore.

38:38.817 --> 38:40.750
