in my own house.

38:40.752 --> 38:44.387
<i>Listen, baby, this</i>
<i>happens all the time.</i>

38:44.856 --> 38:47.657
<i>You guys are close.</i>
<i>You have an important bond.</i>

38:48.360 --> 38:49.526
<i>You'll pull through it.</i>

38:49.528 --> 38:50.960
I was so young when I had her.

38:50.962 --> 38:53.563
I feel like she just doesn't
respect me as a mom.

38:54.666 --> 38:56.933
I feel like her older sister
sometimes, you know.

38:57.502 --> 38:58.735
I--

39:00.372 --> 39:02.339
- I think I might be pregnant.
